section.para:
Using this wizard you can add the next Hibernate annotations to the class:

        @Column,
          @Entity,
            @ManyToOne,
              @OneToMany,
                @OneToOne,
                  @ManyToMany,
                    @MappedSuperclass,
                      @Id,
                        @GeneratedValue ,
                          @Version

listitem.para:
@ManyToOne,
  @OneToMany,
    @OneToOne,
      @ManyToMany - this annotations are declared according to the  classes hierarchy.
